			<p>Lexonomy also supports <a href="https://elexis-eu.github.io/elexis-rest/">ELEXIS REST API</a> - calls <tt>dictionaries, about, list, lemma, tei</tt>. Use your API key as <tt>X-API-KEY</tt>.</p>
